<br>
It's not verant that caused the problem, it's greed, pure and simple. The game reflects alot of Real life. In real life is greed, therefore it is expected in game.<br>
<br>
The only thing that is verant fault in the cleric epic, in my opinion, is the fact there isn't enough bottlenecks. If you were bored and had guild support, you could kill everything in the cleric epic and get all the peices, excpet ragefire, in one day.<br>
<br>
Lord Bergugle (I've killed/camped him 3 times now solo, for clerics that didn't feel like it, because I was bored. I get 2-3 a day normally)<br>
<br>
Seeker in Temple of sulisek Ro: Again, a spawn which, at most, takes an hour to spawn/kill<br>
<br>
Dude in Sol A (forget the name) Again, not a hard camp. takes an average of 5 hours or so, of which i've done numerous times before.<br>
<br>
Ixiblat Fir: the spawner spawns every hour or so if he's killed. Max wait, 2 hours.<br>
<br>
Overking: if he's up, Personally, I can get a raid force down to him within 10 minutes. He's a 2 hour spawn.<br>
<br>
Ragefire: The only spawn that takes over a day to spawn, AND is guaruntee'd to have the peice on him.<br>
<br>
If anything, I'd make a petition to make the cleric epic harder, more botlenecks. Heck, even the rogue epic has longer bottlenecks than the cleric epic. And we all know how fast the rogue epic can be obtained. (if you don't, it was considered an epic factory when it first came out)<br>
<br>
I don't blame verant, I blame the individuals that camp ragefire. If they can't come up with an agreement, then Why should verant have to act like a babysitter? <p><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=25288" Border=0><img src="http://www.mindspring.com/~fitzpp/sigpic1clones.jpg"></a></center></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#333333>- </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower>The Magician's Tower</a><font color=#333333> - </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants>Rants !</a> <font color=#333333> - </font><a href="http://www.magecompendium.com/">The Mage Compendium</a><font color=#333333> - </font>  <br><br><table border=0 align=center><tr><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">Upgrade your account to ezSupporter...</a></td><td><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/spacer.gif" width=15 height=1 border=0></td><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">...and never see another ad or pop-up again</a></td></tr></table><CENTER><!-- START BOTTOM AD SCRIPT -->
